metadata.name: "my skinny bones"
metadata.description:
It's me, you see my life, the skinny bones that speak to you, my life is summed up in this picture, there is no strength left in my body, but I continue anyway, I try to be alive! I'm tired of life, but at the same time I'm afraid of death, being alive is what I'm fighting for right now, not living, just being alive! Art always speaks and this is the best way of communication, I will talk to you with the art as long as I am alive, stay with me because your presence by my side is the only thing that keeps these thin bones alive.  
.
